    <!-- Configure app screen -->
    <string name="config_title">Please take a moment to configure the Salaat times to your requirements.</string>
    <string name="explain_default_config">
        By default Salaat times are configured using Muslim World League calculation
        method, Shafii Juristic for Asr time calculations and makes no adjustment
        for people living in higher latitudes.\n\n
        Other calculation methods include: Karachi, ISNA, Makkah, Egypt, Tehran, Jafri\n\n
        You can choose to use the default settings (don\'t worry you can change them later), or
        configure the Salaat times to your requirements below.
    </string>

